{"tid":1882372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求助 亞航取消左去程航班","createTime":"2020-02-16T08:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T10:51:44.000Z","uid":323056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0374ca25572fdcf0e059d29d5c2fee4b7bad6a77","tid":1882372,"uid":323056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打絲打識得點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係經Expedia 買去泰國來回機票連埋酒店一齊買<br />\n<br />\n亞航send 左個email 嚟話24/2 果班去程機取消<br />\n但回程無講取消<br />\n我打左去Expedia 問 機票要搵番AirAsia 果邊搞<br />\n酒店就可以改到期 <br />\n<br />\nAirAsia 佢比我網上搞取消 但搞左之後睇番行程連回程果班機都睇唔到 有冇人知係點？ 係咪回程班機都會退錢比我？ <br />\n<br />\nAirAsia 淨係得個bot 可以禁 佢地又無email 無hotline...<br />\n聯絡唔到佢地問清楚<br />\n巴打我可以點做好？ 點先問得到係點？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfac16a51b4f7d5f53ba67d87c057ec635118fdf","tid":1882372,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:10:19.000Z","msg":"(借位thx) 請各位開發新戰線 : Youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的: 利用youtube演算法, 增加黃絲channel及文宣曝光機會, 降低藍絲文宣的散播速度, 應對中共KOL 100計劃<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲channel&rarr; like、comment、subscribe、share</span><br />\n藍絲channel&rarr; 不感興趣 /不要推薦這個頻道、開1.2秒close(降低續看率)<br />\n<ins>進一步措施</ins> : 利用家中長輩ac dislike + report藍片 &amp;<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 觀看+like黃片</span> (提高黃片在其年齡層的曝光度)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">【中共最新滲透計劃 : KOL 100】    <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1881621\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1881621</a></span>"},{"pid":"c615f4defc3a4f1101e4f7bc139617f599ab4814","tid":1882372,"uid":288071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:11:29.000Z","msg":"點解唔喺旅遊台問"},{"pid":"28b091978c4a663653cea1e6be9bb99df4c1b754","tid":1882372,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco